Usage:
  ams <command> [options]

Commands:
  help [command]                                                                                                                       Show help for a command
  auth token [--raw|--json]                                                                                                            Exchange Maps token for access token
  geocode [--json] [--limit N] [--file <path>] [--concurrency N] <address>                                                             Geocode an address
  reverse <lat>,<lon> [--limit N] [--json]                                                                                             Reverse geocode coordinates
  directions <origin> <destination> [--mode <transport>] [--eta] [--json]                                                              Get directions between locations
  search [--near "lat,lng"] [--region "n,e,s,w"] [--near-address <addr>] [--no-cache] [--limit N] [--category <cat>] [--json] <query>  Search for places and points of interest
  search autocomplete [--near "lat,lng"] [--limit N] [--json] <query>                                                                  Get autocomplete suggestions for search queries
  cache <stats|clear>                                                                                                                  Manage geocode cache
  snapshot <center> [--zoom N] [--size WxH] [--format png|jpg] [--output <path>]                                                       Generate a static map image
  unified <query> [--near "lat,lng"] [--zoom N] [--output <path>]                                                                      Search and generate snapshot in one command
  ping [--request-id]                                                                                                                  Ping the Apple Map Server
  version                                                                                                                              Show version info

Exit codes:
  0 success
  1 runtime/API error
  2 usage error
